snippet.title: G.I. Joe: Operation Blackout Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Yo Joe! G.I. Joe and Cobra are back. G.I. Joe: Operation Blackout features 12 playable characters, including Duke, Snake Eyes, Cobra Commander, Destro, Roadblock, Storm Shadow and more. Each soldier has their own unique powers and can be customized with a variety of weapons and skins. There’s also multiplayer with modes such as Capture the Flag, Assault and King of the Hill. G.I. Joe: Operation Blackout is available now on PlayStation, 4, Xbox One, and Switch.

https://gijoeblackout.com/

Xbox One: https://t.co/Bch48icwy0?amp=1
Xbox One Digital Deluxe: https://t.co/Bch48icwy0?amp=1
